\"fixed top-0 w-full z-50 bg-surface/80 backdrop-blur-md border-b-2 border-primary-container shadow-[0_4px_0_0_rgba(122,30,30,0.5)] flex justify-between items-center px-4 md:px-16 py-4\"><a class=\"font-[Epilogue] text-2xl md:text-4xl font-extrabold text-primary drop-shadow-[2px_2px_0px_#7A1E1E] tracking-tight scale-90 origin-left\" href=\"/\">FREAK CIRCUS HUB</a><div class=\"hidden md:flex gap-6 items-center\"><a class=\"text-on-surface-variant hover:text-primary transition-colors duration-300 font-[Epilogue] text-base uppercase tracking-widest\" href=\"/characters\">Characters</a><a class=\"text-on-surface-variant hover:text-primary transition-colors duration-300 font-[Epilogue] text-base uppercase tracking-widest\" href=\"/endings\">Endings</a><a class=\"text-on-surface-variant hover:text-primary transition-colors duration-300 font-[Epilogue] text-base uppercase tracking-widest\" href=\"/theories\">Theories</a><a class=\"text-on-surface-variant hover:text-primary transition-colors duration-300 font-[Epilogue] text-base uppercase tracking-widest\" href=\"/walkthroughs\">Walkthroughs</a><a class=\"text-on-surface-variant hover:text-primary transition-colors duration-300 font-[Epilogue] text-base uppercase tracking-widest\" href=\"/lore\">Lore Archive</a><a href=\"https://www.buymeacoffee.com/\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"noopener noreferrer\" class=\"bg-primary-container text-primary px-6 py-2 border-2 border-primary shadow-[4px_4px_0px_#000] active:translate-x-1 active:translate-y-1 active:shadow-none transition-all font-[JetBrains_Mono] text-xs uppercase\">Support the Archive</a></div><button class=\"md:hidden text-primary\" aria-label=\"Toggle menu\"><span class=\"material-symbols-outlined text-3xl\">menu</span></button></nav><section class=\"bg-cream py-32 px-4 md:px-16\"><div class=\"max-w-3xl mx-auto\"><h1 class=\"font-[Epilogue] text-4xl md:text-5xl font-bold text-paper-heading mb-8 underline decoration-blood decoration-4\">Privacy Policy</h1><div class=\"space-y-6 text-paper-text\"><p class=\"italic\">Last updated: January 2025. This document has been reviewed by the Archivist.</p><h2 class=\"font-[Epilogue] text-2xl font-semibold text-paper-heading mt-8\">1. Information We Collect</h2><p>Freak Circus Hub is a static informational archive. We do not require user accounts or collect personal data for core functionality. When you browse our site, we may collect:</p><ul class=\"list-disc pl-6 space-y-2\"><li>Anonymous analytics data (page views, traffic sources)</li><li>Browser type and device information for optimization</li><li>IP address (anonymized where possible)</li></ul><h2 class=\"font-[Epilogue] text-2xl font-semibold text-paper-heading mt-8\">2. How We Use Information</h2><p>Any data collected is used solely for improving the archive experience and understanding which lore sections need expansion. We do not sell, trade, or share personal data with third parties.</p><h2 class=\"font-[Epilogue] text-2xl font-semibold text-paper-heading mt-8\">3. Cookies</h2><p>We use minimal cookies for site functionality and analytics. You can disable cookies in your browser settings, though this may affect certain features.</p><h2 class=\"font-[Epilogue] text-2xl font-semibold text-paper-heading mt-8\">4. Third-Party Services</h2><p>We may embed content from external platforms (YouTube, Reddit) or use analytics services. These services have their own privacy policies.</p><h2 class=\"font-[Epilogue] text-2xl font-semibold text-paper-heading mt-8\">5. Contact</h2><p>For privacy concerns, contact<!-- --> <a href=\"mailto:hello@freak-circus.com\" class=\"text-blood underline\">hello@freak-circus.com</a>.</p></div></div></section><footer class=\"bg-secondary-fixed w-full mt-auto relative overflow-hidden border-t-4 border-dashed border-on-secondary-fixed-variant flex flex-col md:flex-row justify-between items-center px-4 md:px-16 py-8 gap-6\"><div class=\"absolute inset-0 opacity-5 pointer-events-none\"><div class=\"flex flex-wrap gap-4 p-4\"><span class=\"text-xs font-[JetBrains_Mono] border border-black p-1 rotate-12\">ADMIT ONE</span><span class=\"text-xs font-[JetBrains_Mono] border border-black p-1 -rotate-6\">SECTION B</span><span class=\"text-xs font-[JetBrains_Mono] border border-black p-1 rotate-45\">VOID</span></div></div><div class=\"flex flex-col md:flex-row items-center gap-4 md:gap-8 z-10\"><div class=\"font-[Epilogue] text-xl md:text-2xl font-semibold text-on-secondary-fixed\">FREAK CIRCUS HUB</div><div class=\"font-[JetBrains_Mono] text-xs uppercase text-on-secondary-fixed opacity-70 text-center md:text-left\">© 1988-2025 ARCHIVE DATA CORRUPTION DETECTED. ALL RIGHTS RESERVED.</div></div><div class=\"flex gap-4 md:gap-6 z-10 flex-wrap justify-center\"><a class=\"font-[JetBrains_Mono] text-xs uppercase text-on-secondary-fixed-variant font-black underline\" href=\"/privacy-policy\">Privacy Redacted</a><a class=\"font-[JetBrains_Mono] text-xs uppercase text-on-secondary-fixed opacity-70 hover:bg-on-secondary-fixed/10 transition-all px-2\" href=\"/terms-of-service\">Terms of Service</a><a href=\"mailto:hello@freak-circus.com\" class=\"font-[JetBrains_Mono] text-xs uppercase text-on-secondary-fixed opacity-70 hover:bg-on-secondary-fixed/10 transition-all px-2\">Contact Archivist</a></div></footer></main><!--$--><!--/$--><script src=\"/_next/static/chunks/15xrurgzs99gv.js\" id=\"_R_\" async=\"\"></script><script>(self.__next_f=self.__next_f||[]).push([0])</script><script>self.__next_f.push([1,\"1:\\\"$Sreact.fragment\\\"\\n2:I[39756,[\\\"/_next/static/chunks/01xlw8hd842-c.js\\\",\\\"/_next/static/chunks/0d3shmwh5_nmn.js\\\"],\\\"default\\\"]\\n3:I[37457,[\\\"/_next/static/chunks/01xlw8hd842-c.js\\\",\\\"/_next/static/chunks/0d3shmwh5_nmn.js\\\"],\\\"default\\\"]\\n4:I[88589,[\\\"/_next/static/chunks/01xlw8hd842-c.js\\\",\\\"/_next/static/chunks/0d3shmwh5_nmn.js\\\",\\\"/_next/static/chunks/0-edybcnyovi5.js\\\"],\\\"default\\\"]\\n10:I[68027,[\\\"/_next/static/chunks/01xlw8hd842-c.js\\\",\